=E2=80=94 letting autonomous AI bots pay for real-world services (like Goog=
le=E2=80=99s AI models, data tools, etc.) instantly, cheaply, and without a=
ny accounts or subscriptions.</p><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">Right now, AI a=
gents are like super-smart kids with no wallet. They can <em>think</em> and=
 <em>act</em>, but they can=E2=80=99t easily pay for things on the internet=
 because everything requires human logins, credit cards, and subscriptions.=
</p><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">pay.sh (built on Solana + Google Cloud) fixe=
s that:</p><ul><li><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">Agents can now discover and p=
ay-per-use for powerful APIs (Gemini, BigQuery, Vertex AI, etc.) using Sola=
na stablecoins.</p></li><li><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">They pay in crypto =
=E2=86=92 the provider gets paid in normal dollars (fiat) with a full legal=
 license.</p></li><li><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">No accounts. No subscripti=
ons. Just =E2=80=9Cpay as you go=E2=80=9D like a vending machine.</p></li><=
/ul><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">This is the missing piece for the agent econ=
omy to actually explode.</p><h3>Why Solana Wins Big</h3><ul><li><p style=3D=
"margin:10px 0">Insanely cheap &amp; fast: Even at just 1% of its capacity,=
 Solana is already cheaper than big centralized exchanges. At full scale, f=
ees basically go to zero =E2=80=94 perfect for millions of tiny agent trans=
actions.</p></li><li><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">Stablecoins on Solana =3D t=
he best rails for machine payments right now.</p></li><li><p style=3D"margi=
n:10px 0">x402 (a new payment standard) just processed 1 million transactio=
ns in two weeks =E2=80=94 showing real demand is already here.</p></li><li>=
<p style=3D"margin:10px 0">Solana becomes the default =E2=80=9Cmoney layer=
=E2=80=9D for the entire agentic internet.</p></li></ul><h3>The Bigger Pict=
ure aka the AGENTIC ERA</h3><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">3 things are happeni=
ng all at once. </p><ul><li><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">AI agents will write=
 most of the code (GitHub is already preparing for 30x more code because of=
 agents).</p></li><li><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">These agents will need to =
buy compute, data, and intelligence on demand.</p></li><li><p style=3D"marg=
in:10px 0">The ones that can pay instantly and cheaply will dominate.</p></=
li></ul><p style=3D"margin:10px 0">Solana + pay.sh just gave them the walle=
